  "text": "A tactile discrimination task with the 2-AFC procedure [CITATION_1] was designed, and was performed by each participant. Periodic vibrotactile stimulation was delivered using the haptic glove described in the previous section. The experimental session consisted of the presentation of 150 pairs of stimuli divided into 15 sequences, as described in the following.",
